dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents State Assembly Districts for Wisconsin in 2002. [2002 Assembly Districts: Districts as created by the Federal Court Redistricting Decision dated May 22, 2002. The districts were effective as of May 30, 2002, when the U.S. District Court for the Eastern District of Wisconsin issued its decision in Baumgart et al. v. Wendelberger et al. The plan used the statewide municipal ward dataset created by local officials using U.S. Census Bureau's TIGER 2000 data and annexations up to August 1, 2001.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit: https://gis-ltsb.hub.arcgis.com/. For additional information and most current data, please visit https://gis-ltsb.hub.arcgis.com/.
